&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;2&quot;&gt;We are seeking a mission-aligned &lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;2&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;33&quot;&gt;Hardware (Electrical) Engineer&lt;/strong&gt; to drive the design and development of cutting-edge hardware for our Intake product team.&lt;/p&gt;
