&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;7,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;7,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Lead and execute&lt;/strong&gt; the full hardware development lifecycle, from component selection and schematic capture to PCB design and layout.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
