&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Account Executive, Navy&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Shift5&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Shift5 is building the data platform for onboard operational technology (OT). We deliver cybersecurity, predictive maintenance, and compliance capabilities that enable defense and commercial fleets to operate with greater readiness, resilience, and mission assurance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a mission-aligned Strategic Account Executive, Navy to drive growth and mission impact across the U.S. Navy accounts.&amp;nbsp;This role sits at the intersection of sales, mission delivery, and product and will play a critical role in supporting Shift5’s next phase of growth within maritime and naval operations.&amp;nbsp;This is not a transactional sales role. It requires deep mission understanding, executive access, ownership, and the ability to navigate complex DoD environments while driving outcomes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Note:&lt;/strong&gt; This position requires U.S. citizenship due to federal contract requirements and access to controlled information.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and drive end-to-end revenue growth across U.S. Navy accounts in the information warfare domain (e.g., N2N6, NAVWAR, Fleet Cyber Command, DON CIO, DON PCA, etc).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute account strategies aligned to Navy priorities, including modernization, readiness, cybersecurity, and data integration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain senior-level relationships (O-6/O-7, SES, program leadership) across acquisition and operational commands&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify, shape, and close new business opportunities, including large, multi-year programs and contracts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner cross-functionally with Mission Delivery, Product, and Engineering to align solutions with mission needs and ensure successful execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the full sales cycle, from prospecting and pipeline generation through close&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Travel up to 40% as needed to support customer engagement and mission execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and coordinate capture efforts, including RFP shaping, proposal strategy, and stakeholder alignment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as the voice of the customer, informing product direction and go-to-market strategy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Navigate complex procurement pathways including OTA, FAR-based contracts, IDIQs, and subcontracting vehicles&lt;/li&gt;
